Source: lua-posix
Section: interpreters
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Enrico Tassi <gareuselesinge@debian.org>
Build-Depends: cdbs (>= 0.4.23-1.1), debhelper (>= 8.1.3), lua5.1-policy-dev (>= 32), libncurses5-dev (>= 5.9), bsdmainutils, automake, help2man
Standards-Version: 3.9.2
Vcs-Svn: svn://svn.debian.org/pkg-lua/packages/lua-posix
