Package: liblua5.1-posix1
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Pre-Depends: multiarch-support
Conflicts: liblua5.1-posix0
Replaces: liblua5.1-posix0
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: posix library for the Lua language version 5.1
 This package contains the Lua posix library, that includes some posix
 functions like fork, chmod, wait, sleep and kill.

Package: liblua5.1-posix-dev
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Pre-Depends: multiarch-support
Section: libdevel
Depends: liblua5.1-posix1 (= ${binary:Version})
Description: posix development files for the Lua language version 5.1
 This package contains the development files of the Lua posix library,
 useful to create a statically linked binary (like a C application or a
 standalone Lua interpreter).
 Documentation is also shipped within this package.

Package: liblua5.1-curses1
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Pre-Depends: multiarch-support
Conflicts: liblua5.1-curses0
Replaces: liblua5.1-curses0
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: curses library for the Lua language version 5.1
 This package contains the Lua curses library.

Package: liblua5.1-curses-dev
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Pre-Depends: multiarch-support
Section: libdevel
Depends: liblua5.1-curses1 (= ${binary:Version})
Description: curses development files for the Lua language version 5.1
 This package contains the development files of the Lua curses library,
 useful to create a statically linked binary (like a C application or a
 standalone Lua interpreter).
 Documentation is also shipped within this package.
